{
  "stem": "21582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, everyone who's experienced-- it was really-- it stood out simply because of the grand scale of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so we came-- you had, you know, these people dragging through, through, with-- through Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody is, is descending to assemble in this big field.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there are the Germans standing in their leather and their whips.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they are, you know, they, they are absolute masters of your life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was the big selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "What they really did, they told people to line up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And if they tapped you this way, you go this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You, you, you-- then you join the march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If he taps you that way, you, you stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You stay.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You remain.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Fortunately, all four of us-- my mother, my sister, and my father, and I were tapped not to join the march.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But my friend Janka, she was very sick at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She had the yellow jaundice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She was so yellow, so waxen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the Germans pointed for her to go to join the march.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She clutched her pillow, and she yammered, Mama, Mama.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[CRYING] Her mother didn't join her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[CRYING] But when she was gone and the Germans withdrew, her mother went crazy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[CRYING] She just screamed and surrendered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[CRYING] Periodically people said, enough, enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they-- and they-- and they-- they felt that maybe this way, they saved some dignity, that they were so afraid that they are going to become so, so, so, so ravaged.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I remember Janka had a nanny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And that nanny just dressed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She said, I don't want to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She said, I want to look my best.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she dressed up and took her little suitcase as though she was going away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, whatever will be will be.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
